        "cp": "1CP",
        "type": "Response Clade – Battle Tactic Stratagem",
        "legend": "The Skitarii have datamapped every distance, angle and optimised fire field of their ship in advance, and can access this targeting intelligence at will.",
        "when": "Your Shooting phase .",
