        "name": "Beseech the Machine Spirits",
        "text": "At the end of the Move Units step of your Movement phase , the bearer can attempt to operate a Hatchway that is visible to and within 9\" of it, instead of one within 1\". When doing so, if your opponent attempts to prevent it, add the bearers Toughness characteristic to your result of the roll-off , instead of that of a friendly model within 1\" of that Hatchway.",
