        "text": "You can include up to two of the following units (duplicates are not allowed): EPIDEMIUS POXBRINGER SLOPPITY BILEPIPER SPOILPOX SCRIVENER You can include up to three of each of the following units: PLAGUEBEARERS (10 models) NURGLINGS (3 models) You can include up to one of the following unit: BEASTS OF NURGLE (1 or 2 models)"
