        "text": "You can include up to two of the following unit: ROGUE TRADER ENTOURAGE (4 models) You can include up to three of the following unit: IMPERIAL NAVY BREACHERS (10 models) You can include up to six of the following unit: VOIDSMEN-AT-ARMS (6 models) You can include up to one of the following unit: INFANTRY INQUISITOR If you include an INQUISITOR model, you can include one of the following unit: INQUISITORIAL AGENTS (6 or 12 models)"
