        "text": "All of the ADEPTUS ASTARTES models in your Boarding Patrol must be drawn from the same Chapter . You can include up to two of the following units (duplicates are not allowed): INFANTRY CHARACTER (excluding TERMINATOR models) PRIMARCH You can include up to three of each of the following units: ASSAULT INTERCESSOR SQUAD (5 or 10 models) BLOOD CLAWS (5 or 10 models) CRUSADER SQUAD (5 or 10 models) DEATHWATCH VETERANS (5 or 10 models) GREY HUNTERS (5 or 10 models) HEAVY INTERCESSOR SQUAD (5 or 10 models) INTERCESSOR SQUAD (5 or 10 models) PRIMARIS CRUSADER SQUAD (10 models) TACTICAL SQUAD (10 models) You can include up to one of each of the following units: AGGRESSOR SQUAD (3 models) BLADEGUARD VETERAN SQUAD (3 models) COMPANY HEROES (5 models) DEATH COMPANY MARINES WITH BOLT RIFLES (5 or 10 models) DEATH COMPANY MARINES (5 or 10 models) INFERNUS SQUAD (5 or 10 models) INNER CIRCLE COMPANIONS (3 models) PRIMARIS SWORD BRETHREN (5 or 10 models) STERNGUARD VETERAN SQUAD (5 or 10 models) WOLF GUARD (5 or 10 models) WULFEN (5 or 10 models) You can include up to one of the following units: ERADICATOR SQUAD (3 models) HELLBLASTER SQUAD (5 models) You can include up to one of the following units: ASSAULT INTERCESSORS WITH JUMP PACKS (5 or 10 models) DEATH COMPANY MARINES WITH JUMP PACKS (5 or 10 models) FENRISIAN WOLVES (5 models) SANGUINARY GUARD (3 models) SKYCLAWS (5 or 10 models) VANGUARD VETERAN SQUAD WITH JUMP PACKS (5 or 10 models)"
