        "text": "You can include up to two of the following unit: WINGED TYRANID PRIME You can include up to three of each of the following units: HORMAGAUNTS (10 models) NEUROGAUNTS (10 models) RIPPER SWARMS (3 models) TERMAGANTS (10 models)"
