        "text": "Synaptic Web The internal structures of voidships are no obstacle to the insidious reach of the Hive Mind. Units from your army with the Shadow in the Warp ability retain that ability. Units from your army with the Synapse ability retain that ability and gain this one. When measuring whether a unit from your army is within Synapse Range of a friendly SYNAPSE model, Walls and closed Hatchways are ignored."
